                    <p class="font_8" style="font-size:25px; line-height:normal;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:open sans;"><span style="font-weight:normal;"><span style="font-style:normal;"><span><span style="color:rgb(12, 60, 96);"><span style="letter-spacing:0em;"><span style="font-family:wfont_454bc7_528f45cef3c34834b4bba54bd4c25952,wf_528f45cef3c34834b4bba54bd,orig_hero_new_regular;"><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;"><span style="font-size:25px;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

                    <p class="font_8" style="font-size:25px; line-height:normal;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:open sans;"><span style="font-weight:normal;"><span style="font-style:normal;"><span><span style="color:rgb(12, 60, 96);"><span style="letter-spacing:0em;"><span style="font-family:wfont_454bc7_528f45cef3c34834b4bba54bd4c25952,wf_528f45cef3c34834b4bba54bd,orig_hero_new_regular;"><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;"><span style="font-size:25px;">The privacy of your data — and it is your data, not ours! — is a big deal to us. In this policy, we lay out: what data we collect and why; how your data is handled; and your rights to your data. We promise we never sell your data: never have, never will.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

                    <p class="font_8" style="font-size:25px; line-height:normal;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:open sans;"><span style="font-weight:normal;"><span style="font-style:normal;"><span><span style="color:rgb(12, 60, 96);"><span style="letter-spacing:0em;"><span style="font-family:wfont_454bc7_528f45cef3c34834b4bba54bd4c25952,wf_528f45cef3c34834b4bba54bd,orig_hero_new_regular;"><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;"><span style="font-size:25px;"><span class="wixGuard">​</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

